formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1) We have relied on the work of experts who have issued form 1 Architect Certificate and Form 2 Engineer certificate   for construction stage and cost incurred by the promoter for the project Skylights
2) It is the responsibility of the management of the firm to provide Mobile Number and PAN card of customer and we have relied on management confirmation
3) The list of Unsecured Loan account is taken as per data provided by the Promoter of the firm and we have not checked its actual utilization as the necessary evidence are not in possession of the promoter
4) The Figures of Construction cost incurred is derived based on accounting data provided to us for verification and the same is prepared to the best of our knowledge and explanation provided to us.
5) As per the information and explanation provided to us by the promoer, The promoter of the firm has called to various allottee to come for an agreement to sell however out of total  75 units booked till 21/12/2020, 74 units were required to execute Agreement to sale and promoter has already executed ATS/sale deed  with 59 units. Out of remaining 15 units, 8 allottee had made direct sale deed during corona pandemic and other 7     Allottee has not came for agreement to sale till now.
6) Interest paid on secured loan taken for Construction till 21/12/2019 is of Rs. 1,78,19,427 against the estimated Cost of Rs. 1,50,00,000			
7) Interest paid on unsecured loan taken for construction till 21/12/2020 is of Rs. 79,91,612/- as against the estimated cost of Rs. 1,50,00,000			
8) The firm has completed the project and BU has been received on 08/07/2020. The promoter of the firm has already incurred & paid construction cost of Rs. 20,27,92,155 against the estimated construction cost of Rs. 21 Crore.  The promoter is expecting that additional 25 Lacs cost is pending for payment which can be confirmed on reeipt of bill from creditors.			
9) As per the information and explanation provided to us,The promoter had made direct sale deed of the unit to customer wihtout executing Agreement to sale when the B.U. Permission has been received  and the customer demanded to execute sale deed.
10) As per the information provided to us, Encumbrance created on the units are released by the financer only when the customer has made payment in excess of 10 % and hence the data provided in form 3A will show units under encumbrance if the amount received is less than 10 % of booking amount agreed by the prospective customer.
